[gd_scene load_steps=145 format=3]

; SAND — Expanded desert kingdom: dune field, Grand Pyramid with carved
; multi-chamber interior (entrance hall, downward corridor, trap room,
; treasury, burial chamber, secret tunnel to summit), Sphinx-analog,
; obelisk plaza, 3-building ruin complex (Thoth temple, collapsed library,
; Bastet shrine), oasis with tent and camel-analog, quicksand pit, tilted
; broken tower, scattered artifacts, vultures. CSG SUBTRACTION carves
; pyramid interior, obelisk hieroglyphs, ruin archways and windows.
; Spawn: (0, 1, 30) facing north toward the pyramid silhouette.

