; ========== PYRAMID INTERIOR (CSG-carved chambers) ==========
; Layout plan (player enters from south door in tier 1, at around z=-10, y=0):
;   Entrance chamber: center approx (0, 0, -30), 20x14, y=0..6
;   Main corridor: ramp dropping from entrance south end down to y=-6,
;                  tunneling east-west underground
;   Trap room: east of corridor end, at y=-6, 14x14
;   Treasury: further south, at y=-6, 18x14
;   Burial chamber: deepest, at y=-12, 16x16
;   Secret tunnel: narrow shaft climbing from burial chamber up to hatch

; --- Entrance Chamber (CSG-CARVED hieroglyph wall via SUBTRACTION) ---
; The chamber is a CSGCombiner3D: a big sandstone box with cut-outs.
